title: Mike Hollingsworth on Popeye
itunes:title: Mike Hollingsworth on Popeye
description:
Mike Hollingsworth is a talented animator (BoJack Horseman) and a really funny guy. He also loves the movie Popeye. Like, a lot. So do I. Tune in for a rundown of this decidedly odd Robert Altman film.
